    "In that case, the application is focused on the body part to be rehabilitated, so the applications must be Interactive and propose a single task: to rehabilitate that area of the body.",
    "HR is the most useful parameter to extract that data, because it shows the physical effort of the user.",
    "EDA and respiration can also be used.",
    "Standalone wireless HMDs are recommended in the case of monitoring sports performance.",
    "Applications with real-time biofeedback have hardly been developed in the field of Education though they offer many possibilities."
